descriptionHtml:
This is my third and most realistic preset, in contrast to my previous cartoon-esque elven presets.

For your character to look the way I intended, you will require:
[url=http://skse.silverlock.org/]SKSE[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]Racemenu[/url] - by expired6978
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/6709/?]DIMONIZED UNP female body[/url] - by dimon99
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267/?]SG Female Textures Renewal[/url] - by hellosanta
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327/?]SG Female Eyebrows[/url] - by hellosanta
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49279/?]Northborn Scars[/url] - by Northborn
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70363/?]KS Hairdos - HDT Physics[/url] - by Stealthic Khaos
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?tab=1&navtag=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nexusmods.com%2Fskyrim%2Fajax%2Fmoddescription%2F%3Fid%3D13722%26preview%3D&pUp=1]The Eyes of Beauty PLAYER[/url] - by LogRaam

Installation:
1- Place the included file into the following directory : C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\SteamApps\common\Skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\Chargen\Presets.
-If you’ve installed Skyrim somewhere other than the default Steam directory, then replace (C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\SteamApps\common\) with the directory you have placed the game in.
2- Open up Skyrim and type “showracemenu.”
3- In the “Presets” tab, press F9 and select “Adessa”.
4- Re-select the “Sliders” tab and edit the character to your liking.
5- Enjoy!

If you have any advice or suggestions, please post them in the comments or PM me.
author: mmurf
